# Firewall Hardening Lab using pfSense 🔥🛡️

## 📌 Project Overview

This project demonstrates the implementation of firewall hardening techniques using pfSense in a virtual enterprise network environment. The objective is to secure network communications, enforce access control policies, monitor network traffic, and validate security controls through attack simulations.

The lab simulates a small enterprise network where firewall rules are configured to restrict unauthorized access and reduce the attack surface.

---

## 🎯 Objectives

* Configure and manage a pfSense firewall
* Implement network access control policies
* Restrict unnecessary services and ports
* Monitor and analyze firewall logs
* Simulate attacks and validate firewall effectiveness
* Gain hands-on experience with enterprise firewall administration

